 This is an investigational study.

 Bevacizumab is FDA approved and commercially available for the treatment of colon, breast, and lung cancer.

 Its use for the treatment of cancer that has spread to the meninges of the brain or the spinal cord is investigational.

 Up to 25 patients will take part in this study.

 All will be enrolled at MD Anderson.

